ava</surname><given-names>S</given-names></name></person-group><article-title>Wound healing activity of the latex of Euphorbia nerifoliia linn</article-title><source>Indian J Pharmacol</source><year>1996</year><volume>28</volume><fpage>107</fpage><lpage>9</lpage></element-citation></ref><ref id="ref8"><label>8</label><element-citation publication-type="book"><person-group person-group-type="editor"><name><surname>Acharya</surname><given-names>Vaidya Jadavaji Trikamji</given-names></name><name><surname>Acharya</surname><given-names>Narayan Ram</given-names></name></person-group><article-title>Sushruta, Sushruta samhita, Chikitsa Sthana, Visarpa Nadi Stanaroga Chikitsa Aadhyaya</article-title><year>2008</year><volume>17</volume><edition>1st ed</edition><issue>29</issue><publisher-loc>Varanasi</publisher-loc><publisher-name>Chowkhambha Surabharati Prakashan</publisher-name><fpage>468</fpage></element-citation></ref><ref id="ref9"><label>9</label><element-citation publication-type="journal"><article-title>Ibidem Sushruta Samhita(8)</article-title><source>Bhagandara Nidana Adhyaya</source><volume>4</volume><issue>9</issue><fpage>282</fpage></element-citation></ref><ref id="ref10"><label>10</label><element-citation publication-type="book"><person-group person-group-type="author"><name><surname>Goligher</surname><given-names>J</given-names></name></person-group><source>Surgery of the Anus Rectum and colon</source><year>2002</year><edition>5th ed</edition><publisher-loc>Delhi</publisher-loc><publisher-name>A.I.T.B.S Publishers and distributors</publisher-name><fpage>178</fpage></element-citation></ref><ref id="ref11"><label>11</label><element-citation publication-type="book"><person-group person-group-type="editor"><name><surname>Acharya</surname><given-names>Vaidya Jadavaji Trikamji</given-names></name><name><surname>Acharya</surname><given-names>Narayan Ram</given-names></name></person-group><article-title>Sushruta, Nidana Sthana, Bhagandara Nidana Adhyaya</article-title>